weloveclouds.server.services

Interface IMovableDataAccessService

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IDataAccessService
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IReplicableDataAccessService
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MovableDataAccessService, ReplicableDataAccessService

    public interface IMovableDataAccessService
extends IDataAccessService
    A common interface to those IDataAccessService implementations whose underlying storage units can be moved.
